<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title><%- title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/style/all.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&family=Roboto:wght@500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@48,400,1,0"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div
      class="flex gap-[30px] max-w-[920px] bg-white mt-[120px] mb-[100px] mx-auto px-[95px] py-[60px] shadow-[0px_3px_6px_#00000029]"
    >
      <div class="hidden w-[350px] md:block">
        <img
          class="mb-5 md:block"
          src="https://github.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/blob/main/js_week5/main_img.png?raw=true"
          alt=""
        />
        <img
          src="https://github.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/blob/main/js_week5/logo.png?raw=true"
          alt=""
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[calc(100%_-_350px)]">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-1">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined align-middle text-xl mr-1"
            >add_circle</span
          >新增旅遊套票
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-primary w-full h-[3px] mb-8"></div>
        <form class="js_form" onsubmit="return false" novalidate>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap" for="name"
                >套票名稱</label
              >
              <input
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full rounded-t-sm placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
                type="text"
                id="name"
                placeholder="請填寫套票名稱"
                name="name"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_name ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label
                class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap"
                for="imgUrl"
                >圖片網址</label
              >
              <input
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full rounded-t-sm placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
                type="text"
                id="imgUrl"
                placeholder="請填寫圖片網址"
                name="imgUrl"
                pattern="^(?:https:\/\/|http:\/\/).+"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_imgUrl ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap" for="area"
                >景點地區</label
              >
              <select
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary text-[#818A91] w-full rounded-t-s"
                id="area"
                required
              >
                <option class="hidden" value="">請選擇景點地區</option>
                <option value="台北">台北</option>
                <option value="台中">台中</option>
                <option value="高雄">高雄</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_area ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label
                class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap"
                for="price"
                >套票金額</label
              >
              <input
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full rounded-t-sm placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
                type="number"
                id="price"
                min="0"
                step="1"
                placeholder="請填寫套票金額"
                name="price"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_price ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label
                class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap"
                for="group"
                >套票組數</label
              >
              <input
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full rounded-t-sm placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
                type="number"
                id="group"
                min="0"
                step="1"
                placeholder="請填寫套票組數"
                name="group"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_group ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <label class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap" for="rate"
                >套票星級</label
              >
              <input
                class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full rounded-t-sm placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
                type="number"
                id="rate"
                placeholder="請填寫套票星級"
                min="0"
                step="1"
                max="10"
                name="rate"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="js_error_rate ml-[94px] text-red-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-6">
            <label
              class="mr-[30px] text-primary whitespace-nowrap"
              for="description"
              >套票描述</label
            >
            <textarea
              class="bg-[#FAFAFA] border-0 border-b-[1px] border-primary w-full h-[120px] rounded-t-sm resize-none placeholder:text-[#818A91]"
              type="number"
              id="description"
              placeholder="請填寫套票描述 (限 100 字)"
              maxlength="100"
              name="description"
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <input
            class="js_submit block ml-auto px-10 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-xl rounded-[5px] cursor-pointer"
            type="submit"
            value="新增套票"
          />
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#F7F7F7] pb-32">
      <div class="container pt-14">
        <div class="flex justify-between">
          <div class="w-[960px] mx-auto flex items-center mb-[50px]">
            <select
              class="js_filterGroup mr-[30px] rounded md:w-[30%]"
              name="filterGroup"
            >
              <option class="hidden" value="全部地區">地區搜尋</option>
              <option value="全部地區">全部地區</option>
              <option value="台北">台北</option>
              <option value="台中">台中</option>
              <option value="高雄">高雄</option>
            </select>
            <p class="js_filter text">本次搜尋共 6 筆資料</p>
          </div>
          <div id="chart"></div>
        </div>
        <ul class="js_ticketList grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 gap-y-8">
          <li
            class="col-span-4 bg-white shadow-[0px_3px_6px_#00000029] rounded"
          >
            <div class="relative">
              <img
                class="block w-full h-[180px] object-cover rounded-t"
                src="https://github.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/blob/main/js_week5/travel_1.png?raw=true"
                alt=""
              />
              <div
                class="absolute px-5 py-2 bg-secondary text-white text-xl rounded-r top-0 -translate-y-1/4"
              >
                台北
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute px-2 py-[5px] bg-primary text-white rounded-r bottom-0 translate-y-1/2"
              >
                8.5
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-col justify-between h-[calc(100%_-_180px)] p-5"
            >
              <div>
                <h3
                  class="text-primary text-2xl font-medium pb-1 mb-4 border-b-2 border-b-primary"
                >
                  綠島自由行套裝行程
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-5">
                  嚴選超高CP值綠島自由行套裝行程，多種綠島套裝組合，提供台東綠島來回船票、綠島環島機車、綠島民宿住宿，行程加贈『綠島浮潛體驗』以及『綠島生態導覽』，讓你用輕鬆的綠島套裝自由行，也能深度認識綠島在地文化。
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <p class="text-primary">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined align-middle mr-[6px]">
                    error
                  </span>
                  剩下最後 <span id="ticketCard-num"> 87 </span> 組
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-center text-primary">
                  TWD
                  <span
                    class="font-roboto text-[32px] ml-1"
                    id="ticketCard-price"
                  >
                    $1,400
                  </span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios@1.1.3/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/5.16.0/d3.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/c3/0.7.18/c3.js"></script>
    <script src="./assets/js/vendors.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="./assets/js/all.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
